                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500"><strong>Use Case:</strong> Block DDoS attacks on e-commerce platforms.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- ASPM -->
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition">
