                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Application Security Posture Management for comprehensive risk oversight.</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500"><strong>Use Case:</strong> Monitor security compliance across multiple apps.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- CSPM -->
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition">
